### Get access token admin
POST http://localhost:7766/realms/flagforge/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type = password &
client_id = flagforge-frontend &
username = ff-admin &
password = ff

### Get access token user
POST http://localhost:7766/realms/flagforge/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type = password &
client_id = flagforge-frontend &
username = ff-user &
password = ff